American rapper, Calvin Broadus Jr. popularly known as Snoop Dogg, has asked to do a song with Nigerian singer, Tems. He made this known in a video which went viral on Friday. “Yo, Tems, when we gon make a record? You know I’m a fan. I had to get that out the way now let’s get to the set. Let’s make a f*cking hit record girl. You be having my whole family dancing to your s**. I need one with you and you can post that.” he said in the video. 